# Override of root .dockerignore for training builds (src/batch/Dockerfile.train).
# Root .dockerignore excludes src/batch/ and infra/ to shrink the inference image;
# training needs src/batch/. After the src/ migration, all Python source lives
# under src/, so the allowlist collapses to a single !src/** entry plus the
# top-level requirements.txt and pyproject.toml.
**
!src/**
!requirements.txt
!pyproject.toml
src/batch/tests/**
src/**/tests/**
src/**/__pycache__/**
**/__pycache__/**
**/*.pyc
